Detailed Description

This class lets you use any python object supporting the 'sequence' interface as an STL sequence (which lets you make a SequenceWatcher of it).

It holds a reference to the sequence it wraps.

Note that due to the types of references returned (they're a separate object, not a value_type &), iterators cannot support the -> operator ... they only support the * operator.
